\nscenario. We suggest that a more sophisticated treatment of molecular ISM\nstructure, one informed by high spatial resolution CO maps, is needed to link\ncloud-scale models to kpc-scale observations of galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2013 00:01:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
