rest for future accelerators. This contribution\nreviews the development of ingot niobium technology and attempts to make a case\nfor this material being the choice for future accelerators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 5 Apr 2013 14:13:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-08"}
